title: Sushma Swaraj holds talks with Turkmenistan counterpart
article_body: ASHGABAT: External Affairs Minister on Thursday held talks with her counterpart on a wide range of bilateral issues during a transit halt here. Swaraj, on her way to , was received at the airport by Meredov. "Making the most of a transit halt!," Raveesh Kumar, the Spokesperson for the Ministry of External Affairs, tweeted. Swaraj had a good exchange of views on a wide range of bilateral issues, he said. Swaraj is currently on a four-day visit to Kazakhstan, the Kyrgyz Republic and Uzbekistan as part of India's efforts to boost strategic partnership with resource-rich Central Asian nations.
